_:N348a613844f344fdb6ec66663623e35c <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK Space Agency coheres policy, strategy and delivery across the whole of government, driving innovation and delivering world-class space science programmes in partnership with the UK space sector and international partners. </p>\n\n<p>The UK space sector generates an annual income of £18.6 billion and employs 55,000 people across the country.  More generally, space and satellite services are estimated to support wider industrial activities worth £454 billion to the economy, or 18% of GDP. </p>\n\n<p>The UK Space Agency is part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology. We work closely with other departments and research organisations which have equities in space.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/uk-space-agency-annual-report-and-accounts-2024-2025\">Read our latest Annual Report</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
